flavor_text_entries.flavor_text:
A Pokémon that was formed by 108
spirits. It is bound to a fissure
in an odd keystone.

It was bound to a fissure in an
odd keystone as punishment for
misdeeds 500 years ago.

Its constant mischief and misdeeds
resulted in it being bound to an Odd
Keystone by a mysterious spell.

It was formed by uniting 108 spirits.
It has been bound to the Odd Keystone
to keep it from doing any mischief.

It was formed by uniting 108 spirits.
It has been bound to the Odd Keystone
to keep it from doing any mischief.

Son mauvais comportement lui a valu
d’être enchaîné à une Clé de Voûte
par un mystérieux sortilège.

resulted in it being bound to an Odd

１０８この　たましいが　あつまって
うまれた　ポケモン。かなめいしの
ひびわれに　つながれている。

108개의 영혼이 모여서
태어난 포켓몬이다. 쐐기돌의
균열과 연결되어 있다.

Un Pokémon composé de 108 esprits. Il provient
d’une fissure dans une clé de voûte étrange.

Ein Pokémon, das aus 108 Geistern besteht.
Es ist an einen Spalt in einem mysteriösen Stein
gebunden.

Se formó a partir de 108 espíritus. Está unido a la
fisura de una piedra angular mística.

Pokémon formato da 108 spiriti. È stato imprigionato
nella fessura di una Roccianima.

A Pokémon that was formed by 108 spirits. It is
bound to a fissure in an odd keystone.

１０８個の　魂が　集まって
生まれた　ポケモン。
要石の　ひび割れに　つながれている。

５００ねんまえに　わるさをしたため
かなめいしの　ひびわれに
からだを　つなぎとめられてしまった。

500년 전에 나쁜 짓을 했기 때문에
쐐기돌의 균열에
몸이 연결되어 갇혀 버렸다.

Il fut emprisonné dans la fissure d’une clé de voûte
étrange en guise de punition il y a 500 ans.

Es wurde in einen Spalt eines Steins gebannt,
als Sühne für Untaten, die es vor 500 Jahren
begangen hatte.

Como castigo por una fechoría 500 años atrás, está
unido a la fisura de una piedra angular mística.

500 anni fa fu imprigionato nella fessura di una
Roccianima come punizione.

It was bound to a fissure in an odd keystone as
punishment for misdeeds 500 years ago.

５００年前に　悪さをしたため
要石の　ひび割れに
体を　つなぎとめられてしまった。
